nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when image set properties were created.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when image set properties were updated.

nested_items.name: deletedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the image set properties were deleted.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The error message thrown if an image set action fails.

nested_items.name: imageSetArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) assigned to the image set.

nested_items.name: overrides
nested_items.description: This object contains the details of any overrides used while creating a specific image set version. If an image set was copied or updated using the force flag, this object will contain the forced flag.

nested_items.name: forced
nested_items.description: Setting this flag will force the CopyImageSet and UpdateImageSetMetadata operations, even if Patient, Study, or Series level metadata are mismatched.
